{"tid":100031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人鐘意魔戒","createTime":"2017-01-29T16:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:34:55.000Z","uid":49481,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2c3255ed172ec076a3f04d54deaa3182f95a68e","tid":100031,"uid":49481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:05:57.000Z","msg":"頭先睇埋魔戒三部曲 真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n配樂，人設，劇情都係神級 仲有Frodo同Sam真係好Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但睇完有小小唔明 ，最尾Frodo點解要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為劍傷? 但唔係之前俾精靈醫返好啦咩?<br />\n仲有精靈係坐船去邊? 去個邊有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Arwen點解會變返凡人嘅生命 ?<br />\n<br />\n同埋我睇完先發覺Aragorn繼續用班亡靈打埋Mordor 咪得囉 做咩要死咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d8ac4f571b8a43313acc5000663c44568b54b3","tid":100031,"uid":55964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"最鍾意亞拉崗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個第一次睇魔戒真係好震撼，好中意個世界觀，就算大個每次睇都唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21d2491100d25dfdf5befdf1e2f6bef7e05856a","tid":100031,"uid":55964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先睇埋魔戒三部曲 真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n配樂，人設，劇情都係神級 仲有Frodo同Sam真係好Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但睇完有小小唔明 ，最尾Frodo點解要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為劍傷? 但唔係之前俾精靈醫返好啦咩?<br />\n仲有精靈係坐船去邊? 去個邊有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Arwen點解會變返凡人嘅生命 ?<br />\n<br />\n同埋我睇完先發覺Aragorn繼續用班亡靈打埋Mordor 咪得囉 做咩要死咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佛羅多走好似因為想隱世？<br />\n亞玟變凡人因為想同亞拉崗生兒育女過凡人生活，唔想自己望住愛人死亡<br />\n因為亞拉崗同亡靈講左數，只係幫佢地打一場仗<br />\n<br />\n有錯請屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ed74ef7d68ffc24bc98ed897e465ef59d582ec","tid":100031,"uid":12933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"亡靈同亞拉岡打仗因為話打完就解放佢地先幫佢打，其實唔解放佢地班亡靈都吹佢唔脹，但應承咗佢地就算啦，費事走數<br />\n<br />\n費倫多好似因為隻蜘蛛果陣就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe4bf98f45153001e731ebcc43bb603695d3f22","tid":100031,"uid":12933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"Frodo係咪同甘道夫一樣<br />\n其實死左<br />\n但個天話佢未完成任務唔俾佢死住<br />\n一做完就要死？<br />\n<br />\n細個係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e55c15c41cd5475be97b3b9757d2fe27ae6d2b","tid":100031,"uid":49481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Frodo係咪同甘道夫一樣<br />\n其實死左<br />\n但個天話佢未完成任務唔俾佢死住<br />\n一做完就要死？<br />\n<br />\n細個係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔通俾戒靈隊左刀個次就死左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88e7ed85a7d20454692f068e81843cf5aceb128","tid":100031,"uid":49481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭先睇埋魔戒三部曲 真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n配樂，人設，劇情都係神級 仲有Frodo同Sam真係好Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但睇完有小小唔明 ，最尾Frodo點解要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為劍傷? 但唔係之前俾精靈醫返好啦咩?<br />\n仲有精靈係坐船去邊? 去個邊有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Arwen點解會變返凡人嘅生命 ?<br />\n<br />\n同埋我睇完先發覺Aragorn繼續用班亡靈打埋Mordor 咪得囉 做咩要死咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><